com.sciencesakura.dbsetup.csv

Class Import

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sciencesakura.dbsetup.csv.Import
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Operation

    public class Import
extends Object
implements Operation
    An operation which imports a CSV file into a table.

    This operation just uses the Insert operation internal, does not 'upsert'. So almost always you need to use it in combination with Truncate or DeleteAll operations: 

     
 @Before
 void setUp() {
     Operation operation = sequenceOf(
         truncate("user"),
         csv("data/customer.csv").into("customer").build());
     DbSetup dbSetup = new DbSetup(destination, operation);
     dbSetup.launch();
 }
